metadata.name: Nefarious Narwhal #1
metadata.description: A collection of 10,000 criminal narwhals, stealing from the rich in order to help shelter pets. Some traits have been named in memory of pets that our supporters nominated to have memorialized in this collection - Shey, Heidi, Lionhead, Candy, Leo, Chico, Bugsy, Lily, Smudge, Macie Latte, Chopper, Tex, Brutus, Misty, Dizzy, Buster, Malhadinho, and Spencer.
